        "Description": "Good morning, agent 47.\rToday you will arrive at Whittleton Creek in America.\rThere you have to kill four targets:\rHelen West\rJames Burton\rLissy Arlington\rHerbert West.\rThese all have been famous to bake and sell poisoned muffins, And you have been chosen to take them out.\rI will now leave you to prepare.\rGood luck, 47.",
